FBIS3-25555 "drafr036_e_94009" FBIS-AFR-94-036 Document Type:Daily Report 23 Feb 1994 WEST AFRICA Nigeria Official Warns Media on Reporting Military Activities AB1902123094 Lagos Voice of Nigeria in English 1030 GMT 19 Feb 94 AB1902123094 Lagos Voice of Nigeria Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] The chief of training and operations at the Defense Headquarters, Major General Rufus Kupolati, has appealed to journalists to exercise caution in reporting military activities to avoid misinforming the people about the Armed Forces. He made the appeal to journalists during a recent media publication about the Forces in the southeastern part of the country. He also said that reports that link troops movement and other related matters could jeopardize the security of the nation.
